snippet.title: The One Game You Can't Miss: Prepare for Kitten Hero
snippet.description:
Kitten Hero is a fast-paced, action platformer were you play as a litle cat (very cute by the way), trying to rescue his friend from a evil artificial intelligence.

Check it out:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1813440/Kitten_Hero/
